Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:04.48,comntry,,0,0,0,,WARNING: this commentary contains spoilers. Watch after completing the series.\NAlso, commentary tracks are not held to the same translation standard as regular dialogue tracks. This is a rough TL.\N{\1c&H9AF8BC&}The guest this time is the seiyuu for {\fnArial Unicode MS\fs50}志筑仁美{\fn\fs}(Shizuki Hitomi):\N{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs50}新谷良子{\fn\fs}(Shintani Ryouko) - affectionately called {\fnArial Unicode MS\fs50}りょーこ{\fn\fs}(Ryooko).
