Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:14.53,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,it's {\i1}Mahou Shoujo Madoka{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs76}☆ {\fs\fn}Magika{\i0} volume four, episode seven {\i1}Can You Face Your True Feelings?{\i0} audio commentary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:16.16,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Me, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:18.62,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yup! With the role of Homura, Saitou Chiwa, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:18.62,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&}Yup! With the role of Homura, Saitou Chiwa, {\alpha}and—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:20.83,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Yup, arranged with the role of Shizuki, Shintani Ryouko!
