Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:24.33,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Yaaay *clapclap*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:25.79,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, she's Shizuki-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:27.34,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That is Hitomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:27.34,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, Shizuki Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.34,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:28.34,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,The kanji is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.09,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, it was hard to read at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:33.51,chiwa,,0,0,0,,And now it's completely serious! From ep6.
