Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:40.89,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, like you'll get deceived by this cute little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:42.64,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Really, he's scary~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:42.81,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:41.85,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:43.60,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Cute QB.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:47.02,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Really, now, the story moves forward a great amount...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.27,chiwa,,0,0,0,,with this thing's bad parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:48.82,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:50.65,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This completely white thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:49.52,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:53.57,chiwa,,0,0,0,,has a lot of darkness associated with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:55.95,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Well, Ryouko-chan has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:55.70,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:57.12,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:57.12,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.70,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Right here is when he becomes like that. Right? (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:00:59.08,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:00.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:01.08,ryooko,,0,0,0,,It isn't normal, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:01.79,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's there, that's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:04.29,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, he begins to get a bit evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.17,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Now, I wonder what we should ask, Ao-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:10.25,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right? Ah, um... What do you think of Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:11.46,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Eh? (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:13.17,chiwa,,0,0,0,,How about for auditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.17,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Then, auditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:13.55,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:17.64,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Ahh, the topic of auditions is okay? It's a bit of a sorrowful topic though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:19.10,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, mm, I think it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:25.69,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I didn't originally ask for Hitomi's role. After the other roles were probably no good, I went to Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:28.65,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see, I see. So you didn't intend to get Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:28.65,ryooko,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&}Ah, I see, I see. So you {\alpha}didn't intend{\alpha&HFF&} to get Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:30.15,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:29.36,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ehh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:30.15,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:33.11,ryooko,,0,0,0,,At first it had changed around, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.11,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ahh, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:33.69,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Also, QB.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.40,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But that seems to be about true for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.57,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Right? Seems so, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.16,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Then, there was Kyousuke, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:39.82,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, there was Kyousuke too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:39.41,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Kyousuke, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:43.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,As for me I took QB, and one more... so it was Kyousuke, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.58,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahohoho, right, right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.58,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:53.59,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I took QB and Kyousuke, and um... I was told by Urobuchi-san to try out Homura, so I took Homura, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:46.75,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:55.84,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, that's why, it seems like everyone tried a lot of characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:59.72,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I was told "What do you want to do yourself?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:56.51,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:02.47,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That was probably, Sayaka and Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.10,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ahh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:03.39,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:08.44,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I asked to please try them out. Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:10.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That was a bit of a special part.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.27,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Right, but Hitomi was a bit of a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.19,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Hitomi, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:18.70,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Because Sayaka and Homura are pretty different, right? Obviously. So when I took Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:22.87,ryooko,,0,0,0,,"What kind of tone should I take," I thought. Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.95,chiwa,,0,0,0,,How did you interpret the role of Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:32.92,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Somehow, when I first took Sayaka and Homura, there was a slight overview of the scenario, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:39.68,ryooko,,0,0,0,,When I saw that, I knew that she'd be a character who'd change Sayaka quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:42.64,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Somehow or another, she had that image.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:44.93,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Then, I found out that I thought she was a pretty wicked girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:46.35,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, it was always covered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.35,chiwa,,0,0,0,,She might just be the most bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:48.35,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.27,ryooko,,0,0,0,,After I was told, I thought "Ah, what should I do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:56.90,ryooko,,0,0,0,,When I had first seen the script, I thought she was like a tidy {\i1}ojou-sama{\i0}, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.90,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm, that's right. Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:06.54,ryooko,,0,0,0,,At this point, I thought that if she was going to move out of righteousness to grant her love, then I sort of had a guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:11.50,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Well, my image of her was that of a sincere {\i1}ojou-sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.79,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, she really seems like a delicate person, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:12.96,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Sincere and pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:14.79,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.80,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I'd say she somehow or another had that image, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.05,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ahh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.68,chiwa,,0,0,0,,She had that feeling, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.38,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:20.68,ryooko,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.34,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But then, starting here? Is this where it starts?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:27.10,chiwa,,0,0,0,,At this time, I'd say "Oh, Hitomi's dirty."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.10,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.47,ryooko,,0,0,0,,In a word, yes. (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.69,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,But with her "black" expression, you wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.15,chiwa,,0,0,0,,What is different will differ, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.35,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Somehow, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:36.77,ryooko,,0,0,0,,She's upfront, but also too much of a thief, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.19,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.82,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right. Right, right. But, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:43.24,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Um, that's true for their age range though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:41.70,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:48.49,chiwa,,0,0,0,,They're middle schoolers, so they'll end up hurting each other's feelings and such. You understand when seeing that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.03,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:53.67,ryooko,,0,0,0,,When you think about the fact they're middle schoolers, you can really say that they're amazing, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.67,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.67,ryooko,,0,0,0,,For Sayaka, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:56.63,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.50,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.80,chiwa,,0,0,0,,They're strong, aren't they? Super strong girls, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:02.18,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That is, somehow, she's a "properly righteous and strong" person...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:05.51,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just that she probably doesn't know much about Sayaka's circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:05.51,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.93,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But there's no helping that, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.60,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Well, it has begun now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.60,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:15.48,chiwa,,0,0,0,,From the eyes of Madoka herself, her view of the world has completely changed now, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.44,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.57,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I believe she is seeing absolutely different things now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.57,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow, there was that conversation before, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:29.33,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's why around here, Madoka goes into a constant decline, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:28.66,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.29,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Madoka and Sayaka are constantly depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.66,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, you don't really see smiles anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:34.79,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:35.12,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's true, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.17,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Sayaka has been feeling dull...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.59,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Riiiight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.59,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Sayakaaa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.96,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That is, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:43.76,chiwa,,0,0,0,,She begins to converse with Homura a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.01,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mm, mm, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.18,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right. Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:51.89,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Around here, what is it, when Homura-chan comes, she gives Madoka a slight bit of relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:59.15,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Like at this time, by talking to each other, they give each other stability and a bit of relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.57,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It's as if though, at least for now, they won't break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:01.57,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:05.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But around here Homura's sense of herself is extremely shaken up, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.57,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.32,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:15.37,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Really, just like this, Madoka's direct interactions build up, and she endures it but she can never respond to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:20.42,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I think that a lot of people who aren't sure about her circumstances are watching this, since you don't know until the end, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:27.13,chiwa,,0,0,0,,When you know it, and listen to her lines once again, there's a sort of pitiable feeling the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:25.09,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:25.76,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.01,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Riiight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:31.22,ryooko,,0,0,0,,From episode one, it's pretty painful to watch from Homura's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:29.97,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right–right–right–right–right
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:35.43,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's why, each and every episode, Homura-chan is unexpectedly shaken up, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.89,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:44.53,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Although, that's... perhaps not in this episode yet, but they add moments where she's extremely shaken up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.57,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mm, mm mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.32,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.61,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But I can't that say until later. Even though it's commentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.53,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.53,ryooko,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:48.82,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's done on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.57,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Ahh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:49.78,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,On purpose~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.66,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.33,ryooko,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.74,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.75,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.17,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's true for Madoka as well, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:58.58,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:01.88,chiwa,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of things you can't say. Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:00.79,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&}Thesre are{\alpha}a lot!{\alpha&HFF&} of things you can't say. Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:01.50,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mm, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:05.21,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,You can't say anything about Madoka until the very, very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.59,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.63,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It's a "can't talk about it" mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.89,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm, there are a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:14.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But, well... at this point, everyone did it on purpose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.39,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:14.56,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.52,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Did it on purpose~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:16.52,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&}Did it {\alpha}on purpose~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:17.81,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Even for Hitomi, after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:18.48,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.40,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ne? Ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:19.98,ryooko,,0,0,0,,It was on purpose, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.98,chiwa,,0,0,0,,On purpose, you know. (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:21.98,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&}On purpo{\alpha}you know~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.53,ryooko,,0,0,0,,But you know, I think Homura is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:26.44,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,mmm
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:26.44,chiwa,,0,0,0,,mm, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:28.57,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Somehow, you know, she's extremely strong, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.99,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That is true~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:34.99,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But perhaps, really, when I was acting as her, I could see her strength, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.25,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I thought she was also very weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.25,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Delicate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.21,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.46,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It feels like she has no choice but to become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:43.38,ryooko,,0,0,0,,In the end, I guess that's really how it is if you have something to protect, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:46.38,ryooko,,0,0,0,,There is strength... but you may be weak as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.72,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But you know, lately I've been having thoughts that, in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:52.80,chiwa,,0,0,0,,the exhausted people who say "Help me!" are the really strong ones, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.39,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Ah, but you know, that just might be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.68,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.01,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:07:00.06,chiwa,,0,0,0,,The people who don't say that are the ones who are actually weak–This is true for Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.06,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.35,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.44,chiwa,,0,0,0,,She doesn't say anything, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:09.28,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I really think this, but when you get cocky about yourself, or think of yourself as strong, or place too much on yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:13.03,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That entraps you, and it's actually weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.03,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:18.06,chiwa,,0,0,0,,In that sense, Hitomi is actually the opposite, she's really "resolute,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:23.71,chiwa,,0,0,0,,but she acts very fluffy and girlish, when in reality she's extremely strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.45,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.59,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I consider her strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.50,chiwa,,0,0,0,,She is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:30.42,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow, she seemed a bit strong in those scenes that imply she's studying to become empress, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.13,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Somehow... that's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.64,chiwa,,0,0,0,,She properly has confidence within herself too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.43,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.64,ryooko,,0,0,0,,She does, she does, she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:34.14,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Hauum~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.85,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I sort of want to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.85,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,want to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:36.85,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm, right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.10,chiwa,,0,0,0,,As a girl, it's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:38.10,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.39,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Since I'm a person who would cry when given the chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:38.47,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.31,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:41.56,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.73,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's one part I think is amazing about Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:43.73,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:45.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I think she's amazingly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:50.78,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This has been mentioned before, but it feels like Hitomi will be the most happy in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.41,ryooko,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.53,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right? I think that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:55.45,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Probably, girls like that will properly grab hold of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.37,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I think so. (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:56.78,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:08:03.83,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I feel as if though I aspire to be like her. It's an ideal image for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:03.83,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.04,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:07.38,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then... the one Ao-chan loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.42,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,The one I love. It's Kyouko-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.42,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Kyouko~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.34,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Cute, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.76,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Kyouko-tan is the absolute best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.51,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Nice, isn't she~?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.76,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I love Kyouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.14,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord1.7}Riight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:14.72,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord1.7}Dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:18.06,chiwa,,0,0,0,,And then you know, Aipon's play of her is extremely nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:18.43,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Neee?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.10,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord1.7}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.05,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:18.97,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's a bit playful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.47,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.22,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:25.40,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,This, what is it... it's like she isn't trying to be cool, but she's still REALLY cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.40,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.52,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's amazingly nice~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:30.03,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then, since she always has her heated temperature turned on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.03,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:30.99,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's really nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.11,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord1.7}That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:37.45,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This part—During the recording for this part of the show, it was always like "Sayaka Magika!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:41.83,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, I thought "Sayaka Magika."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:40.95,ryooko,,0,0,0,,(lol) Sayaka Magika, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.95,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It was always said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:41.83,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:42.33,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.50,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:44.25,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:44.96,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:53.55,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,But right here, the slight discrepancy in these two's sense of what's "correct" gives off a very human sense of contrast between them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.30,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,And this art here is wonderful, isn't it? Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:09:00.51,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Really, I'm taken aback by this kind of atmosphere each and every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.10,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.52,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:01.52,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.06,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It's like "HWAAA!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:03.98,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:07.73,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I'd say it's... cute, but scary, and a little bit enchanting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:08.56,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.27,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:14.65,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This is true for Kyouko's topic of discussion right now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:19.66,chiwa,,0,0,0,,There really is justice born from anguish, but it gets thrown off a bit and breaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:20.58,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.58,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:20.87,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.58,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:28.42,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But, when she takes a departure from justice, she begins to go into denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.42,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:28.92,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.21,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.21,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:34.67,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's why in this story, you can really feel everyone's sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.22,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, it hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:44.18,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right. But you know, somehow at the very end, this is relatively true for all of the characters. They all, umm, probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:48.85,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Between being ruined or becoming refreshed, they end up being ruined, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.56,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:52.27,chiwa,,0,0,0,,They're shaken up to such an extent, everyone cries...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:56.11,chiwa,,0,0,0,,At this point I'd say that everyone is falling into ruin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:56.99,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mmm, mm, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.16,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.37,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.62,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That is another part of this story...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.16,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah—Yeah. I can't say it (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.96,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Everyone is definitely carrying some regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:09.17,chiwa,,0,0,0,,From there, a path of regeneration isn't really chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:14.55,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's why, throughout the entire story it feels like everyone resonates with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:15.38,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:20.72,chiwa,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of things like that. A lot of cases where people choose to fall into ruin from a regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:25.64,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Later, it's like receiving help would have been all right, when you think about it afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:28.69,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Surely, you will grow from that experience, when thinking about it afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.81,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, like you won't repeat the same thing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.48,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:32.15,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.61,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,But you know, from the despair becoming a witch—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:35.94,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah–eh, uhh mm, tte–
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.07,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:41.32,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,So, when they become one, it's extremely "Ahhh..." feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:42.78,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:43.91,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.75,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's why even when things that have a forward-looking attitude are said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:51.04,chiwa,,0,0,0,,like Kyouko-tan's conversation right here, they're still always holding sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.04,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:51.79,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:58.92,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow, Kyouko-tan is giving it her all, but she can't properly obtain what she's aiming for... that hurts too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.43,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.43,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.80,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.26,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right. Actually, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.89,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Madoka's family is properly depicted,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:11.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Sayaka and Hitomi are people who also have a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:15.40,chiwa,,0,0,0,,In comparison, all the of the mahou shoujo are pretty much alone, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.40,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.40,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:20.70,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then, I believe there is a contrast between those people, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:28.33,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Unexpectedly, the people who have others giving them protection are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:35.29,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then, Kyouko, Homura, and Mami-san, the people who are alone, are brighter spirited and look forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:35.63,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:39.76,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Umm, well, Homura isn't bright spirited, but she's the one looking ahead the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:44.51,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That contrast left a huge impression on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:54.31,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's why, for the people who are protected by family or such, probably, they are somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.98,chiwa,,0,0,0,,They depend on other people and show weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.94,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then there are the ones who don't depend on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:00.32,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:00.74,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.28,chiwa,,0,0,0,,They aren't hung up on their past,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:06.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,but that past hurts so, so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.20,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Since they all stood up by themselves, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.29,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:07.66,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:11.29,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Moreover, there is their age, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.29,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.29,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:14.25,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's why they seek friends, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:17.17,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That is true for Homura, who is constantly seeking friends. Same with Mami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:17.92,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.09,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's actually true for Kyouko, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:19.84,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:19.84,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:20.67,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.17,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Kyouko~~ {\fnArial Unicode MS}♡{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.30,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Cute, Kyouko~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.59,chiwa,,0,0,0,,What's this, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.01,chiwa,,0,0,0,,You love her, don't you, Ao-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.22,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I love her, you know~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.64,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I understand it. Kyouko is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.76,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,She's nice, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:33.81,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,What is it... You could say she has an antiheroic style, yet she's aiming for "justice" more than anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.48,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.10,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Very human-like, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.06,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:46.03,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Even though she aims for an overall justice that she believes in, she has to fight to overcome aspects of her own unjust self...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.69,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:48.62,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow... I think that hurts a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:54.21,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Really, I find this difference between Kyouko and Sayaka's reasons for fighting amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:53.83,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.21,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Riiight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.08,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I think, "That's amazing!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:13:04.05,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Somehow, Kyouko is fairly sour, but she's actually the one acting in others' interest the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.21,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:09.72,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Sayaka is constantly like "Kamijou-kun, Kamijou-kun" but then in the end might've been doing it for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:12.02,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That contrast between the two is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.60,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:12.85,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:14.56,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Really, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.06,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It successfully felt like a woman's viewpoint, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.56,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:17.81,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:18.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:25.15,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ryouko-chan, you acted as Hitomi, but other than Hitomi, were there any completely unrelated roles you liked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.24,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Riiight,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:31.95,ryooko,,0,0,0,,well, looking at it objectively, then Kyouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.20,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mmmm. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.20,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mm, I think it's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.75,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mmmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.33,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Kyouko is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:38.13,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Well, looking at it objectively, Madoka is the one I understand the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.54,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.54,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:40.21,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:41.67,chiwa,,0,0,0,,You still don't really know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:41.67,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:48.51,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Then in the end, as the person inside Hitomi, after this, it's a bit... She isn't shown much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:52.56,ryooko,,0,0,0,,So I haven't seen how the other characters develop in the after recording stages.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.56,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I see, I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:56.56,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I'd say Madoka is the number one character who is still very mysterious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.60,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I see, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.61,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I'm already... "Madoka Love."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.94,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.03,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Right, I thought that might happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:07.78,ryooko,,0,0,0,,So I haven't actually seen what happens at the very end yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:11.41,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I want to know about Madoka so badly it hurts. (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:16.46,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Well, Madoka is really the most normal girl, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.46,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.92,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,She's the one who blunders about the most, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.50,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,in response to that, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.29,chiwa,,0,0,0,,At the end, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:22.92,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:26.05,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It feels like it completely transcended the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:35.43,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,In the world, there are people who properly voice themselves, and then there are people who are apprehensive about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:38.52,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,When the indecisiveness and silence of those who are apprehensive disappear, it's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.77,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.69,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Ahh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That is certainly true, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.48,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,True for Mado-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.82,chiwa,,0,0,0,,People who have bad circumstances end up being good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.74,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, they're good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:46.53,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Ahhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.78,chiwa,,0,0,0,,The ones floating about are like little kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.03,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,The little floating kittens are cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.70,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol) Right. It's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.70,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.08,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, she's come, finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:00.04,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This everyday life is kind of... relieving, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.25,ryooko,,0,0,0,,A bit relieving, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:00.92,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:01.54,ryooko,,0,0,0,,A bit, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.50,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, I find it scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.13,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:06.00,ryooko,,0,0,0,,By now you'd call it scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.71,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Looking at it now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:11.89,chiwa,,0,0,0,,How did the people around you perceive Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:19.23,ryooko,,0,0,0,,How did that go, um... Director Shinbou said "You can do this," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:28.24,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Somehow, you know... this really... Looking at it afterward, especially to the fans...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:30.78,ryooko,,0,0,0,,You know? I don't really stand out that much (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:31.53,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:34.53,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Hitomi herself might not stand out that much. (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:38.45,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I think that being her seiyuu is amazing, truly wonderful, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.26,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Really, what is it... eople properly watching this series...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:47.80,ryooko,,0,0,0,,They know the views of the multiple characters it commands, especially those of Madoka and Sayaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:53.66,ryooko,,0,0,0,,But as for Hitomi, she's standing in a position where she doesn't know much about Madoka or Sayaka's circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:56.89,ryooko,,0,0,0,,She's a girl going for her own justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.22,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.39,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I think that doesn't go so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.06,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:04.61,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,But you know, the viewpoints on Hitomi differ between girls and guys, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.27,chiwa,,0,0,0,,They may differ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.61,ryooko,,0,0,0,,They're probably different, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:08.19,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Looking from a girl's viewpoint, it's pretty "Uwah!" but... you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.19,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.53,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That sort of feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:09.53,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:13.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,From a guy's viewpoint, it might just seem pretty terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:12.49,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:15.24,ryooko,,0,0,0,,It might feel like she's snatching him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:20.33,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But, everyone is really like "that," right? It's sort of like... what fairness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.16,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.83,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Like she is raising her public image a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:23.83,ryooko,,0,0,0,,No—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:29.05,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Somehow, Sayaka hasn't been boiling over very much, but this is kind of like a fire starter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.05,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mm, how's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:34.43,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,There is something like that too, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.43,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.09,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:39.31,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But you know (lol) really, she just decides on the timing herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.31,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Right! That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.52,chiwa,,0,0,0,,One day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.73,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Hitomi has decided, just one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.85,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,B—But they're still only fourteen years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.19,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.73,ryooko,,0,0,0,,It's honorable, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.52,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.57,ryooko,,0,0,0,,It's fair and square and it's honorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:57.62,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But you know, this girl's ability to look forward makes you think "Ah wow, she's so confident in herself!" It's enviable isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.41,ryooko,,0,0,0,,She has strength, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:58.78,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:16:59.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:16:59.70,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.08,ryooko,,0,0,0,,She's a strong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:02.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord1.5}Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.08,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:09.21,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then, Sayaka is the type of girl who's bright and energetic, but has no self-confidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.80,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I really understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.67,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:18.97,ryooko,,0,0,0,,In this work, the contrast between any two characters is really interesting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:17.89,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:22.31,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Relating to that, this work is one with a lot of conversations that hurt, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.02,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:27.15,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Th–This girl is just scary now~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:33.82,ryooko,,0,0,0,,If I was told this, I'd definitely be more like Sayaka - "Ah what3jaefja3jafd."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.86,ryooko,,0,0,0,,If I had to pick one, I'm actually closer to Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:40.45,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow, this... She isn't really wrong, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:43.00,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,The spot it hurts is surely painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:46.96,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's why Sayaka is all mixed up inside of herself, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:53.42,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But everything happening at this timing is incredibly bad for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:58.43,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's why, even if she's saying something that is fair and square, it's still like "Ehhh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:59.80,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Sayaka would be like "Ehh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:02.47,ryooko,,0,0,0,,It's like if this happened a bit earlier, it might've been a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:05.98,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But you know, that's... they're children, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.06,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That means they won't give too much previous notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:13.44,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,But somehow, thinking about what happens after this, I believe that Hitomi is also a really big victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.06,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.53,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Guess so~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.03,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.40,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But we haven't watched that far yet, so it's off-limits, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.57,ryooko,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.57,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,R–Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:22.94,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow, weak people will be taken under someone's wing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:27.96,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,even for strong people, until they truly become strong, they also rely on support...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:32.17,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I think that as a rule, you can't say it's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:38.76,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This story hopes that you dislike Hitomi more and more here. That's the feelings it adds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:40.89,ryooko,,0,0,0,,There is such a meaning, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:43.81,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I get really into my own role, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.47,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:46.64,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That is very amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:47.48,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's nice, it's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:48.39,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.39,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.98,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, this part... {\fnArial Unicode MS\fs80}(´；ω；`)ｳｩｩ {\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.52,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I really understand it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.61,ryooko,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yaa{\i0}, I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.82,ryooko,,0,0,0,,It's got a more heavy resonance to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:59.91,chiwa,,0,0,0,,And then you know, Eri's play, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.61,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.62,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It hurts, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.07,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.87,ryooko,,0,0,0,,This is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:03.87,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:09.54,ryooko,,0,0,0,,But during after recording, at this point, every time I saw her like this, I thought "Sorry~"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.50,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.50,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.17,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I was always thinking that (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.17,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.92,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mou{\i0}, this is cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:19.13,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:24.47,chiwa,,0,0,0,,At this time, Madoka is really kind, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:27.35,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I think she's a girl that does it well! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:32.06,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,She isn't just acting here. The fact she actually feels and accepts it is amazing. That's what I think (lol).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:35.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,She is able to do this, but she just quietly accepts it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:35.73,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:38.82,ryooko,,0,0,0,,She's there when she wants her, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.99,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, you know that's important for being friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:41.74,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:41.74,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:48.16,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow, in her class, she doesn't really stand out, but she can really read the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:50.41,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That point of Madoka really does stand out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.54,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mm, mm, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.54,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.75,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I'd say that is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:54.92,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.67,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord1.5}That's right, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.34,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:03.55,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right here, Sayaka has her own circumstances going on. She's sorting things out for herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:07.06,chiwa,,0,0,0,,and Madoka understands that, so she's staying quiet, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:07.89,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:07.89,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:12.98,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Even still, she holds feelings of wanting to help her, but for right now she'll stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:17.48,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Amazing. I think that a 14-year-old knowing so much about relationships with others is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.15,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.15,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:26.45,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Before this conversation, when talking about the relationship of "those three," it's really like Madoka wants to protect Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:27.91,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.04,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Really, three girls are difficult together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:30.87,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.12,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Difficult, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.71,ryooko,,0,0,0,,In that regard, having a childhood friend who's a boy would be a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:36.63,others,,0,0,0,,Neee~? Ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.09,ryooko,,0,0,0,,It really is a blessing, then. (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.71,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord1.5}A boy, huh? Ah, difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.13,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.59,chiwa,,0,0,0,,And, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:44.34,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:45.14,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm, it has come—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.22,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This part DEEPLY MOVES ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.56,ryooko,,0,0,0,,This gives me goose bumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:49.72,ryooko,,0,0,0,,It's too cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.39,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,This is coo—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:53.52,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I thought "So this kind of thing has come," this kind of presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:54.69,ryooko,,0,0,0,,It surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:55.85,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's like it's in shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:59.23,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,This! How it's a bit brighter, so you can properly see the art.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.40,ryooko,,0,0,0,,This is quite cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:02.53,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right, they properly drew all the art, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.11,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,This is super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:05.03,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.07,ryooko,,0,0,0,,This is cool, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:08.62,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Then, what is this, this part has Sayaka's true feeling—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.58,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Riiight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:11.33,chiwa,,0,0,0,,The colors become a bit more dull...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.00,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:12.87,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:14.96,ryooko,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord1.5}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:14.96,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:19.38,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then if that's the case, you could say that Sayaka is actually stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.42,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That condition, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.51,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:21.51,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord1.5}Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:26.38,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow it's like "Being a hero hurts, huh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:26.38,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:28.80,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,and then there's the fact she uses a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.80,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, she has received help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.10,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:40.40,notes,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs55}あんこ{\fn\fs}(Anko) - Anko is Kyouko's nickname in the online JP community.\NIt was given to her because they read her name wrong in early magazine scans.\NUsually when people post things saying {\fnArial Unicode MS\fs50}「あんこ」{\fn\fs}, you'll see a reply like {\fnArial Unicode MS\fs50}「あんこじゃねえ！きょうこだ！」{\fn\fs}(It isn't Anko! It's Kyouko!)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.77,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Anko~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:34.77,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's Kyouko-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.60,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.44,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Everyone is pretty quiet right now, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.52,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,But it's commentary though, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:40.40,ryooko,,0,0,0,,It's too amazing, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:47.08,ryooko,,0,0,0,,When I read the script, it said she had a "crouching start," which made me laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:50.28,ryooko,,0,0,0,,But then when I saw it on air, it was a little bit too cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:53.70,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I felt a bit embarrassed at myself for initially laughing. (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:54.83,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It was actually cool, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:57.62,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Right, right. Like "Ah, so it's like this."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:03.55,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, this part of the show is really like S–Sayaka time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:05.34,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Super Sayaka Time {\fnArial Unicode MS\fs100}☆{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:07.47,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It hurrrts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.14,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It hurts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:10.35,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:10.35,ryooko,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:11.10,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:13.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no, you were just doing your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:13.56,ryooko,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:14.89,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.89,0:22:22.69,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, for having a hand in creating this work.... Ryouko-chan, what do you admire?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:27.28,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Mmm, right, somehow, really... Mm, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:35.08,ryooko,,0,0,0,,This might be getting a bit too detailed, but in order to make such an extremely brilliant world, the process of it turning darker;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:37.87,ryooko,,0,0,0,,the transformation of that sort of presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:44.24,ryooko,,0,0,0,,For example, it had what you'd call the "{\i1}mahou shoujo{\i0} image," especially the whole "{\i1}kira{\i0} bright sparkly" part of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:47.67,ryooko,,0,0,0,,but then it strayed THAT far away from it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:53.14,ryooko,,0,0,0,,When doing a seiyuu's job, you really felt the difference in how you had to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.14,0:22:53.97,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Oh, ohh—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:55.97,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Amazing, to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:00.40,ryooko,,0,0,0,,In that sort of way, your heart flows out...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:04.73,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I'd say there's growth, but properly, there are also things that do not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:09.53,ryooko,,0,0,0,,That sort of... molding of each person... I think of it as it deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:11.03,ryooko,,0,0,0,,I watch it every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.49,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:16.33,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Man, seriously. "What's going to happen after this?" REALLY piques your interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:17.00,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:17.83,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:20.29,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Commentary is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:20.29,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:21.50,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yup. Next time who'll be on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:22.38,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:24.71,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ao-chan, you okay? You look like you're about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.71,ryooko,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:26.50,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Next time is—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.80,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Next time Taniguchi-san will be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:28.80,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.05,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Is that so? (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.05,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:31.13,ryooko,,0,0,0,,It was there just earlier, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:32.84,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahh ::garbled mess::
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:35.85,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Next time Taniguchi-san will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:35.85,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yees
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:36.14,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:38.68,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I think he will be someone you'll want to hear talk from here on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:41.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, then, Ryouko-chan, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:41.56,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:41.56,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:43.10,ryooko,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
